name: Mario Martin
review_text: De esto pueden ver mas resenas de otros clientrs. Las gerentes o jefas que manejan al personal en caja de este McDonalds en Sant Cugat (por ejemplo las del pasado domingo 28 de diciembre una chica gordita y otra delgada rubia con gafas) tratan de manera despota y autoritaria a sus empleados y manejan el restaurante a capricho. Ademas se unen contra otros y tratan a su personal con comentarios como "!quitate de ahi!" o por cualquier aclaracion "ya veras lo que te dice el jefe" poniendo su caprichosa actitud hundiendo a chicos nuevos con gritos del tipo "!muevete que ahi no haces nada!" "!Tu para esto no vales!" Como si fueran alguien importante en el mundo que a lo mejor no tienen ni estudios, solo un trabajo basico en un restaurante donde disfrutan hundiendo a sus companeros hombres. Incluso van hablando mal de personas que pasan por el restaurante a otra gente de Sant Cugat. Horrible.
review_translated_text: You can see more reviews from other customers. The managers or supervisors who run the cashiers at this McDonald's in Sant Cugat (for example, the ones from last Sunday, December 28th, a chubby girl and a thin blonde with glasses) treat their employees in a despotic and authoritarian manner and run the restaurant on a whim. They also gang up on other employees and treat their staff with comments like "Get out of there!" or, for any clarification, "You'll see what the boss says to you," displaying their capricious attitude by undermining new employees with shouts like "Move it, you're not doing anything there!" "You're no good at this!" As if they were someone important in the world, when perhaps they don't even have an education, just a basic job in a restaurant where they enjoy undermining their male colleagues. They even go around badmouthing people who come to the restaurant to other people in Sant Cugat. Horrible.
response_from_owner_text: Gracias por tus palabras Mario Martin, por favor, escribenos a atencionconsumidor@es.mcd.com describiendo tu caso con mas detalle. Vuestro feedback es muy importante para que podamos mejorar.
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you for your feedback, Mario Martin. Please write to us at atencionconsumidor@es.mcd.com describing your case in more detail. Your feedback is very important for us to improve.

name: Izan Ostenero Jou
review_text:
Hago esta resena en comparacion a los otros Mc Donald's debido a que a mi parecer este tipo de restaurantes no son muy saludables por lo tanto no deben de tener una valoracion muy alta.
Comparandolo con los otros restaurantes de su sector, es un establecimiento muy bien ubicado y que destaca por su limpieza y su gran manera de trabajar. La gente que trabaja es muy agradable y te intentan facilitar siempre que tu estes comodo comiendo, en mi caso tuve un problema con la hamburguesa y los empleados me atendieron y solucionaron el problema sin ningun tipo de inconveniente.
Me voy contento del lugar.
review_translated_text:
I'm writing this review in comparison to other McDonald's restaurants because, in my opinion, these types of restaurants aren't very healthy, so they shouldn't have a very high rating.
Compared to other restaurants in its area, it's a very well-located establishment that stands out for its cleanliness and excellent work ethic. The staff is very pleasant and always tries to make sure you're comfortable eating. Mes sentido despreciado por parte de servicio del McDonald's nunca mas volvere a este y espero que esta resena sea viral para que no vuelva s repetir.
review_translated_text:
I ordered through McAuto and received terrible service. First, the woman serving me was rushing me to order repeatedly.
Immediately afterward, when they gave me my order, they made a mistake with all the drinks.
The MacFlurry they ordered was melted and the presentation was terrible.
I then grabbed it and politely asked if I could change it because the presentation was terrible and it seemed like I was studying in poor condition. In response, she told me that as of today, I know things are going well, so if I don't like it, I should go to McDonald's and get my act together and have her stir the ice cream with a swipe in my face.
I felt more than disdained by the McDonald's service. I will never return here again, and I hope this review goes viral so it doesn't happen again.

Hoy..de nuevo nos venimos a casa sin patatas. Hay que revisar  la compra antes de salir...

review_translated_text:
Every time we buy through McAllen, most of the time we're missing our orders... or chips, or sauces, or dessert... they're very quick to place orders and don't seem to listen.
Today... again, we came home without chips. We have to check our shopping before leaving...

Today, thanks again for leaving me without dinner. Another mistake in the order. It's definitely a sign for me to stop eating junk food sometimes, like today, when I'm coming back from a trip and I don't have any food at home. Thanks for being so competent. I won't be back.

I asked if everything was there or if something was missing, they said everything was there, and I left without checking. When I got home, the deluxe fries were missing. name: Albert PS
review_text: El servicio Mcauto es un desastre. De las ultimas 10 veces se habran equivocado en 7 tranquilamente. Vas porque les hace gracia a los crios pero el servicio ha bajado muchisimo en los ultimos anos. Les pides big Mac sin queso y te lo ponen sin nada y con queso por poner un ejemplo. Y no solo en el de Sant Cugat, el de Ripollet lo mismo.
review_translated_text: McAfee's service is a disaster. They've easily made a mistake 7 out of the last 10 times. You go because the kids find it funny, but the service has declined dramatically in recent years. You order a Big Mac without cheese, and they give you one with cheese and nothing else, for example. And not just in Sant Cugat, the Ripollet one is the same.

Una lastima como ha bajado la calidad del servicio, la semana pasada fui con el coche a buscar 3 menus, no podia creer tanta lentitud, tardaron en salir a la ventanilla una eternidad y el dependiente muy poco agradable, le pedi que no me pudiera ketchup y me miro como si pidiera la luna...por supuesto habia ketchup en la bolsa.
Habria acabado antes entrando por mostrador, lo dicho pesimo servicio

19 sep 2021 volvemos y siguen igual o peor, argumentan k solo son 2 pax, pues que pongan mas un domingo hora punta
Y eso que el pedido te lo haces tu y el pagp
review_translated_text:
It's a shame how much the service has gone downhill. Last week I drove there to pick up three meals, and I couldn't believe how slow it was. They took forever to come to the window, and the clerk was incredibly rude. I asked him not to add ketchup, and he looked at me like I was asking for the moon... of course, there was ketchup in the bag.
I would have been quicker just going in at the counter. Like I said, terrible service.

September 19, 2021: We went back, and they're the same or worse. They argue that there are only two people allowed, but they should add more on a Sunday during rush hour! And that's even though you place the order yourself and pay for it.

Anyway...

review_text: La camarera es una maleducada, nos echo a mi y mi acompanante a gritos, por no llegar a otros extremos. Lo mas normal y logico seria que pongan vallas o cintas alrededor de las mesas y de los bancos, y mas en plena pandemia.
review_translated_text: The waitress is rude; she yelled at my companion and me, just to avoid going to the other extreme. Just because we had placed our bags on the terrace table was enough to upset them. The most normal and logical thing to do would be to put up barriers or tape around the tables and benches, especially in the midst of a pandemic.

review_text:
He ido hoy, viernes 29, a las 21:15, hora punta.
La verdad es que tengo que decir que han trabajado TODOS Y TODAS con muy buena coordinacion. Desde fuera se veia mucha cola pero no he tardado nada en poder hacer el pedido en el Mcauto. Muy bien organizado.
Ademas, he de resaltar que las bolitas de pollo estaban realmente excelentes. Enhorabuena  a todo el equipo que estaba trabajando a esa hora.

I went today, Friday the 29th, at 9:15 pm, rush hour.
I have to say that everyone worked very well together. From the outside, there was a long line, but it didn't take me long to place my order at the McAllen Drive-Thru. Very well organized.
I also have to highlight that the chicken balls were truly excellent. Congratulations to the entire team working at that time.

review_text: Habia pedido una hamburguesa sin cebolla sin pepinillos sin tomate i sin mostaza la primera vez me la llevan con cebolla la segunda vez me la llevan con pepinillo tomate i mostaza i la tercera vez que lo pido pago mas por el beicon i me la traen sin beicon encima eh visto que hacian la hamburguesa sin guantes
review_translated_text: I had ordered a hamburger without onion, without pickles, without tomato and without mustard. The first time they brought it to me with onion. Tienes servicio de McAuto, ademas de un pequeno aparcamiento para coches, parque infantil, y mesas preparadas para familias. They give you plastic cups, and you have to clear the table and throw away your trash. On top of being expensive, the food is very low quality. In short, just like all fast-food restaurants.

It's a McDonald's...
But this one gives you colder food than others, and its customers are dirtier, since they leave the trays on the tables and the staff doesn't clean them.
It's good enough to satisfy a craving, but if I can go to another one, it's better. The one in Sant Cugat is better.

name: Miguel Angel Munoz Martinez
review_text:
McDonald's es una cadena de comida rapida que contiene demasiadas calorias, osea que no esta bien ir siempre. Pero...A quien no le gusta disfrutar de la comida rapida? Si quiere ir a un McDonald's, este es mi favorito de la zona. Cuenta con un parque exterior para ninos y aparcamiento para coches, tambien tenemos una gasolinera justo al lado que...Creamos que no da un punto a favor.
Aparte, si usted no es de la zona, puede aprovechar para ver una ciudad muy bonita como es Sant Cugat, y si es deportista tiene cerca una muy buena zona. Yo suelo ir en bicicleta, y despues de hacer un poco de deporte paramos y nos pedimos o un desayuno (por cierto, buenisimos) o unas patatas de 1EU
review_translated_text:
McDonald's is a fast-food chain that contains too many calories, so it's not a good idea to go there all the time. But... who doesn't like fast food? If you want to go to McDonald's, this is my favorite in the area. It has an outdoor playground for children and parking, and we also have a gas station right next door, which... I don't think is a plus.
Also, if you're not from the area, you can take advantage of the opportunity to see a very beautiful city like Sant Cugat, and if you're sporty, there's a great area nearby. I usually go by bike, and after exercising a bit, we stop and order either breakfast (delicious, by the way) or some EU1 fries.

A disgrace!!!!

Yesterday we went with family and three kids, about 15 or 16 years old, with their bikes on the tables, smoking joints. Out of four words they said, three were swear words, and they weren't even used.

I won't go back!!!!!!
